Table 19. Supplemental data for 106 large county governments

a/ Population figures are from the Bureau of the Census, Annual Estimates of the Resident Population for the United States, Regions, States, and Puerto Rico: April 1, 2010 to July 1, 2017 (September 2018).
b/ "Total general expenditure" excludes utilities, county-operated liquor stores, and insurance trust benefits.
c/ "General functions only" FTE excludes utilities and county-operated liquor stores.
